tafsir[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,"Yaa-Siin: yewtere sugu …óee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah."
  36,2,"Alla woondirii Alqur'aana, nde Aayeeje mun √±e√±aa, nde sikke aliraa yeeso e …ìaawo mayre."
  36,3,"Pellet, an Nulaa…óo, ko a jeyaa…óo e …ìe Alla nuli e jeyaa…ìe Mun …ìen, fii ko yamira bajjin…óingol Mo, rewa Mo Kanko tun."
  36,4,"A wonii e laawol focciingol, e sari'a √±ii…ìu…óo, jipporii…óo ka Joomi maa, On Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, Hinnotoo…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  36,5,"A wonii e laawol focciingol, e sari'a √±ii…ìu…óo, jipporii…óo ka Joomi maa, O Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake Hinnotoo…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  36,6,"Alla jippiniriinde e maa…óa, fii a jertinir nden yim…ìe, …ìen woni aarabee…ìe …ìe Nulaa…ìe araano e mun, ko jertina …ìe: …ìen ko welsindii…ìe e gom…óinal e tawhiidi. Ko non kala mofte …óe jertineede ta∆¥ondiri e mun wa'ata, haa …ìe hatonjina e Nulaa…ìe ko jertina …ìe."
  36,7,"Gom…óii konngol lepte jojjirii e ma…ì…ìe, immorde ka Alla, …ìaawo nde salii gom…óinde goonga ka Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe addani kan, …ìe lutti e keeferaaku. ∆Åen …óon gom…óintaa Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe gollirtaa ko …ìen addi e goonga."
  36,8,"Hi…ìe wa'i wa …ìen …ìe kolommbooje falaa e daa…óe mun, juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen renndina daade mum en les bahe mum en haa tawa ko maa …ìe mbaawna faanude ko*e mum en ka kammu. ∆Åee …óoo kadi ko kolmbiraa…ìe e gom…óingol Alla, …ìe yankinantaa- ko Mo, …ìe jippintinortaako fii Makko."
  36,9,"Men wa…ói yeeso ma…ì…ìe heedo e goonga kan, …ìaawo kadi heedo, Men hippi gite ma…ì…ìe …óen e yi'ugol goonga, wa…ói …ìe yi'ataa ko nafata …ìe. ∆äum le, ko tawde …ìe ha…ì…ìitike luttugol e keeferaaku."
  36,10,"Hino fota e …ìee heefer…ìe salii…ìe goonga, foti a hul…ìin …ìe an Muhammadu, maa a hul…ìinaali …ìe; …ìe gom…óintaa ko addu-…óaa kon, immorde ka Alla."
  36,11,"Ko nafitorta jertinaango maa ngon tigiri, ko on ja…ìu…óo Alqur'aana, o gollitiri ko woni e mayre, o huli Joomi makko ka yeewi. Awa wewlinir kala siforr…óo …óum, wonnde Alla yaafanto …ìe junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, O ye…óa …ìe mbarjaari mawdi √ëalnde Darngal, woni naatugol Aljanna."
  36,12,"Ko Menen woni wuurnitoo…ìe maay…ìe …ìen, fii hasbugol √ëalnde Darngal, Men winnda ko …ìe ardini kon aduna e golle bon…óe maa mo∆¥∆¥e, e batteeji ma…ì…ìe heddinoo…ói …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe, wano sadaaki ilooji, maa bon…ói ma…ì…ìe heddinoo…ói, wano keeferaaku. Gom…ói Men moftii kala huunde, e deftere …ìanngunde, nden woni alluwal reenaangal ngal."
  36,13,"An Nulaa…óo, piyan …ìee fennoo…ìe satta-feeree…ìe misal ngal …ìe waajitora, fii yim…ìe saare, nde Nulaa…ìe arunoo e mun."
  36,14,"Nde Men nulunoo e ma…ì…ìe Nulaa…ìe …ói…ói ka arannde, fii ko nodda …ìe e wootin…óingol Alla rewa Mo, …ìe fenni …ìen …óon …ói…ói. Ontuma Men semmbiniri …ìen, Nulaa…óo tata…ìo, …ìe wi'ani yim…ìe saare nden: ""Menen …óoo tato, ko men Nulaa…ìe e mo'on, fii noddugol on e wootin…óingol Alla, jokka sari'a Makko on""."
  36,15,"Yim…ìe saare nden jaabitii Nulaa…ìe …ìen: On laataaki, si wanaa ko on …ìanndinke wano menen, huunde on …ìuraa men. Kadi, Jom-hinaranke on jippinaali hay wahayu e moo…óon. On wonaali, si wanaa ko nodditotoo…ìe fenaande."
  36,16,"Nulaa…ìe …ìen tato jaabitii …ìe, …ìe wi'i: Joomi amen no anndi, wonnde pellet, ko men Nulaa…ìe e mo'on, on yim…ìe ndee saare. ∆äum yonii men hujja."
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wanaa yottinirgol e moo…óon, no …ìanngiri. Men feere fewnugol on."
  36,18,"Yim…ìe saare nden wi'itani Nulaa…ìe …ìen: Men hiitorii on kataa. Si tawii non on ha…óitaaki noddugol e tawhiidi, ma men yagginir on fi…óugol on kaa∆¥e haa maayon, lepte muusu…óe kadi memira on immorde e amen."
  36,19,"Nulaa…ìe …ìen kadi wi'itani …ìe: Kiite mon …óen, hi…óon wonndi e majji, sabu yeddugol mon Alla ngol, saloo jokkude Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen. E ko si on anndinaa- ma fii Alla, non kiitino…óon? Tigi on, ko on yim…ìe fantinoo…ìe e faggitagol geddi."
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ìuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, o ari himo yaccora kulol wata yim…ìe makko …ìen fennu Nulaa…ìe …ìen, …ìe kammbirana …ìe warugol e lorgol e ma…ì…ìe. O wi'i: ""Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, kori jokkee gom…óinon …ìee Nulaa…ìe."
  36,21,"Onon yim…ìe am, jokkee …ìen …ìe …óa…ì…ìirtaa on njo…ìdi ko …ìe yottinirta e mon kon, …ìe woni fewnaa…ìe e kon ko …ìe yottinirta e mon, immorde e wahayu Alla. Kala wa'u…óo non, haray mo hanndi e jokkeede."
  36,22,"Gorko on laa…ìani …ìe reedu, o wi'ani …ìe kadi: E ko ha…óata lam rewugol Alla tagu…óo lam on? Ko ha…óata on, onon kadi, rewugol tagu…óo on On, Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon, immintine…óon fii njo…ìdi?"
  36,23,"Hara mi jogitoto tagaa…ói Alla …óin rewetee…ói gaanin Makko? Si woni Jom-hinaranke On muuyanii lam bone, tefoore …óin rewetee…ói duncantaa lam hay huunde, wanaa poo…óugol nafa, wanaa du√±ogol loraa, …ói waawaa kadi dan…óndugol lam bone mo Alla muuyani lam, si mi arii maayude e keeferaaku. ."
  36,24,"Si wonii mi jogitike rewetee…ói gaanin Alla, haray ontuma, mi wonii e faljere fee√±unde; tawde mi rewii ko handaa e reweeede, mi acci rewugol hanndu…óo e reweede On."
  36,25,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min on mi gom…óinii Joomi men en denndaangal, kori nananee lam. Anndon mi tefaa e ko kammbiranton lam wareede. Kono …óum ha…óaali …ìe warugol mo! Alla naadi mo Aljanna."
  36,26,"O teddiniraa …ìaawo sahimbineede makko, wi'aneede: Naatu Aljanna. Nde o naati ton, o yi'i neemaaji mun, o yelorani yim…ìe makko …ìen wiide: Haaniino yim…ìe am …ìen fennu…ìe lam wari …ìen, …ìe annda ko mi he…ìi e haforaneede junuubi, e teddungol ngal Alla ye…ói lam, fii no …ìe gom…óinira, no mi gom…óiniri, …ìe warjoree no mi warjoraa."
  36,27,"O teddiniraa …ìaawo sahimbineede makko, wi'aneede: Naatu Aljanna. Nde o naati ton, o yi'i neemaaji mun, o yelorani yim…ìe makko …ìen wiide: Haaniino yim…ìe am …ìen fennu…ìe lam wari …ìen, …ìe annda ko mi he…ìi e haforaneede bakkatuujii, e teddungol ngal Alla ye…ói lam, fii no …ìe gom…óinira, no mi gom…óiniri, …ìe warjoree no mi warjoraa."
  36,28,"Men hatonjinaano e halkirgol yim…ìe makko fennunoo…ìe …ìen wari mo, e koneeli Malaa'ika, …ói Men jippinirta ka kammu. Tawde fii ma…ì…ìe no hoyani Men diini …óum. Ko Men e…ì…ìirnoo halakuyee ma…ì…ìe on, ko haacaango immorde ka kammu, wanaa jippingol Malaa'ika ko lepte …ìe."
  36,29,"Halkeede yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa haacaango wooto, ngo Men wuurti e ma…ì…ìe, tawi …ìe tallii hay gooto heddaaki, fii ma…ì…ìe gasii. No …ìe wa…ótiniri non, ko wano yiite hu…ì…ìunoonge, nge √±ifi, hara ba…óte magge heddaaki."
  36,30,"Ee ninse jeyaa…ìe fennunoo…ìe, ee hayrere ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, tuma …ìe yi'oyta lepte …óen! Ko tawde …ìe woniino ka aduna ma…ì…ìe, Nulaa…óo kala arunoo…óo …ìe immorde ka Alla, …ìe wa…ótayno mo jalnori, …ìe jalkita mo. Ba…ótane ma…ì…ìe …óen wonti ninse √ëalnde Darngal, fii ko …ìe fantini kon e bannge Alla."
  36,31,"E …ìee fennoo…ìe jalkita Nulaa…ìe yi'aali …ìe waajitora mofte adinoo…ìe …ìe? ∆Åe annda …ìen …óon maayiino, …ìe artataa aduna han kadi. ∆Åe yahdii e kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe. Wonnde Alla yo…ìitoyay …ìe …óum."
  36,32,"Mofte …óen fow wonaali, si wanaa moo…ìoytee…ìe ka Amen √ëalnde Darngal, tuma …ìe immintinaa, fii yo…ìitugol …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe."
  36,33,"Hujja ummital ngal no woodani fennu…ìe …ìen: e leydi yoorundi hokki ndin, Men jippini to…ìo e mayri, immorde ka kammu, Men fu…óini e mayri nooneeji pu…ói, Men yaltini nooneeji e gabbe, e nder …óin pu…ói, fii ko yim…ìe …ìen √±aama. Yo …ìe anndu non, wuurnir…óo ndin leydi …óon non, ko hattan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ìe."
  36,34,"Men wa…ói e ndin leydi ndi Men jippini to…ìo e mun, gese le…ó…óe tamarooje e inabuuje. Men …ìulliti ton …ìulli ndiyam, ko …óe yarniree."
  36,35,"Men wa…óiri …óen gese, fii no yim…ìe …ìen √±aamira e majje, immorde e kon ko Alla neemini e ma…ì…ìe, hara …ìe yannganaaki …óum. E …ìee yettirtaa Alla e …óii neemaaji …óon, rewugol Mo Kanko tun, gom…óina kadi Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen?"
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii Alla, O toowii. On fu…ó…óu…óo nooneeji …óin fow: gila e pu…ói e le…ó…óe, haa e wonkiiji yim…ìe …ìen, tawde O wa…óirii …ìe deyel e gorel, e kon ko …ìe anndaa fii mun, e tagu Alla ngun ka njorndi e maayo ekn."
  36,37,"Hujja goo wonanii yim…ìe …ìen e fii wootin…óingol Alla, tawde Me…óen na…ìira ndaygu ngun, na…ìugol √±alorma on, adda jemma on, tuma Men sortata √±alorma on e makko, Men wa…óta …óum niwre, haa yim…ìe …ìen naatii e mayre."
  36,38,"Maande goo hollaynde …ìe gootaagu Alla ngun, ko ngee naange dogaynge haa e √±ii…ìirde nge Alla anndi e…ì…ìoore mun, nge ha…óta …óon. Nden, ko e…ì…ìoore Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake On, Anndu…óo Mo huunde e fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun wirnanaaki Mo."
  36,39,"Maande goo kadi tinndinnde e gootaagu Alla senii…óo On, ko nduu lewru, ndu Men e…ì…ìani jipporde jemma kala. Ndu fu…ó…óora toksuru, hooti ndu mawna, hooti ndu fan…óita, haa ndu wa…ótinira wano baa≈ãal tamarohi e noone mun ka soy…óugol e ka hi…ó…óugol."
  36,40,"Maandeeji naange ngen e lewru ndun, e jamma on e √±alorma on, ko Alla elti …ói. ∆äi ha…ótanaa yawtugol ko …ói e…ì…ìanaa kon. Wanaa naange ngen woni ko waawi hewtitorgol lewru ndun, waylugol dogudu magge maa na…ìugol ndaygu magge, wanaa jemaa on kadi ha…ótanaa aditagol √±alorma on, ado o lannude. ∆äi fow majji non, e kala koode e ruugay…ói, ko eltanaa…ói laawi heerii…ói."
  36,41,"Maande goo wonanii …ìe e fii gootaagu Alla ngun, e ko O neemini kon e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, wonnde Men roondike da…óunoo…ìe …ìen ndiyam tuufaana …óam, e geyngol Aadama ngol, fewndo Nuuhu, ka laana hebbiniranooka taguuji Alla. Hari tagu kala e resondirayngel e mun no roondaa e ka laana."
  36,42,"Maande goo wonanii …ìe e fii gootaagu Alla ngun, e ko O neemini e jeyaabe Makko …ìen kon, wonnde Men taganii …ìe sugu laana Nuuhu kan, ko …ìe wa…ó…óoo."
  36,43,"Si Me…óen yi…óunoo, Men yoolayno …ìe; hara faabo woo alanaa …ìe ontuma, wanaa da…óndoowo …ìe e kon ko Men haajani …ìe."
  36,44,"Si wanaa hara Men yurmira …ìe da…óndugol …ìe yoolagol, Men accira …ìe fii no …ìe dakmitora haa e happu, mo …ìe yawtataa, belajo'o, …ìe waajitoray …ìe gom…óina."
  36,45,"Si …ìee sirkoo…ìe …óuurnii…ìe e gom…óingol wi'anaama: rentee e ko sutani…óon ka laakara e ca…óeele mun, rentoron e aduna fe∆¥∆¥oowo, belajo'o, Alla neeminira on yurmeende Makko nden. Kono …ìe ronki wa…óde …óum, …ìe …óuurnii fii mun."
  36,46,"Tuma kala nde Aaya Alla tindin…óe e wootin…óingol Alla, heertinana Mo dewal nagl, ari e …ìee sirkoo…ìe sa…óta-feeree…ìe, …ìe wonay …óuurnii …ìe mo, salii …ìe waajitorde mo."
  36,47,"Si sa…óta feere'en …ìee wi'anaama kadi: walliree waasu…ìe …ìen e wondu…ìe …ìen jawle mon …óe Alla arsiki on …óen. Ko …ìe jaaborta, ko wiide gom…óim…ìe …ìen: kere men √±amminay on taw…óo si Alla muuyuno, O √±amminayno mo? Men lunndotaako muuy…óe Makko …óen. Onon …ìee gom…óim…ìe, on wonaali, si wanaa e faayere …ìanngunde, wo…ó…óitiinde goonga."
  36,48,"Heefer…ìe yeddu…ìe ummital …ìen no wi'a: ko honnde tuma woni ngal ummital, si tawii onon …ìee gom…óim…ìe, on laatike goongu…ìe e …óum?"
  36,49,"∆Åee fennu…ìe ummital habbaaki, si wanaa wuttaandu aranuru ndun ka allaandu, ngun juha…ìe, fewndo ka …ìe yeddondirta fii aduna, immorde sooda yeeya, e rema reena ekw."
  36,50,"Si ngon haacaango ma∆¥inoyii…ìe, …ìe waawoytaa wasiyagol ontuma, wanaa fere fii ruttitoyagol ka cuu…ói e ka …ìeynguure ma…ì…ìe; ko …óon fii ma…ì…ìe lannata, ka …ìe sokolooji mum en fii aduna."
  36,51,"Wuttee …ói…óa…ìun ka Allaandu, …ìe fow …ìe yalta e genaale ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe he√±ora ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, fii hasbeede yo…ìee."
  36,52,"∆Åee heefer…ìe yeddunoo…ìe ummital nin…ìe, …ìe wi'a: Ee hayrere amen! Ko hommbo immini men e genaale amen? ∆Åe jaabee: ko …óum woni ko Alla fodunoo, wonnde pellet, wa…óay; Nulaa…ìe …ìen goonginii e ko …ìe yottiniri …óum kon, immorde e Joomi ma…ì…ìe."
  36,53,"Fii immintineede ka genaale ngol wonaano, si wanaa ba…óte wuttaandu …ói…ìa…ìuru ndun, tawi tagu ngun fow addaama laakara ka Amen, fii hasbeede."
  36,54,"√ëaawoore nden √ëalnde, ko nun…óal wa…óirta, tawde onon jeyaa…ìe …ìen, on too√±irtaake …ìeydaneede bon…ói maa …óuytaneede mo∆¥∆¥i, hay huunde. Ko yo…ìirte…óon, ko njo…ìdi kon ko gollayno…óon aduna."
  36,55,"Yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen √ëalnde Darngal, pellet, …ìe wonoyay e nder neema, yejjitinoowo …ìe kala huunde, hakkee neemaaji √±ii…ìu…ói, …ói …ìe yi'oyta. ∆Åe neeminora …ói weltaare."
  36,56,"Hi…ìe dakmito kam…ìe e genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e hoore dan…óe, ley …óow…óe yaajeendi Aljanna."
  36,57,"Hino woodani …ìe ka Aljanna ton, noone kala e …ìi…ó…ìe le…ó…óe laa…ìu…óe: immorde e inabu, e ∆¥ibbe, e rummaana. Hino woodani …ìe kadi, kala ko …ìe lamndotoo e muuyanteeji maa nooneeji neema. Ko …ìe lamndii woo …óum, …ìe he…ìay."
  36,58,"E hoore neemaaji ma…ì…ìe …óin fow, hino woodani …ìe kadi, konngol kisiyee, immorde e Joomiraa…óo, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe. Si O salminii …ìe, …ìe wonay e on kisiyee, noone kala. ∆Åe he…ìa hiwraango, …ìurngo kala hiwraango darja."
  36,59,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen wi'anee √ëalnde Darngal: sertee non e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, haanaa ka …ìe jillondira e mon, tawde njo…ìdi mon, no seedi e njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe, sifaaji kadi wano non."
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mo'on, Mi ha…óiri on, onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen, e konngol Nulaa…ìe Am …ìen, wiide on: wata on …óofto seytaane, faggitagol noone kala e keeferaaku maa geddi? Tawde pellet, kanko seytaane, ko o ga√±o mon …ìanngin…óo ngayngu. Ko honno haqqil…óo …óoftorta ga√±o mun …ìanngin…óo ngayngu?"
  36,61,"Mi yamiri on kadi, onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen, wonnde yo on rewan Min tun, hara on kafidaali Lam e go…ó…óum. Ko rewugol Lam Min tun ngol, …óoftoo Lam, woni laawol focciingol, …óowayngol e welayee Am e naatugol Aljanna. Kono on wa…óaali ko mi ahodunoo e mun kon, Mi yamiri on."
  36,62,"Gom…óii seytaane majjinii tagu …óuu…óungu e mon. E on wonaano …ìe haqqille mun yamiraynoo …óoftagol Joomi mun, rewa Mo Kanko tun, …óe rentina on e …óoftagol seytaane, taw…óo ko ga√±o fe√±√±inan…óo on ngayngu?"
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge wonano…óon fodaneede ngen aduna, sabu keeferaaku mon ngun. Hari hinge wirnaninoo on, kono hannde, e hino nge, on yi'irii nge gite mon."
  36,64,"Naatee e magge hannde, mee…óiron nnuleeki magge, sabu ko yeddirayno…óon Alla kon, ka nguurndam mon aduna."
  36,65,"Hannde, Men notay e kunndule ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wonta mboboo…ìe, hara …ìe waawataa yeddude geddi e keeferaaku ko …ìe wonunoo e mun kon. Juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yewta Men ko …óe huuwi aduna, koy…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen kadi seeditoo e kon ko …ìe wonunoo e faggitaade e geddi."
  36,66,"Si Men yi…óuno, Men mehayno gite ma…ì…ìe …óen, hara …ìe yi'ataa, …ìe adondira e laawol ngol, fii lummbitirgol ka Aljanna. Kono …ìe wo…ó…óondirii e …óum, tawde gite ma…ì…ìe …óen mehaama."
  36,67,"Si Men yi…óuno kadi, Men waylayno fii ma…ì…ìe, Men femmpira …ìe koy…óe …óen, hara …ìe hippataa sottude e nokku ma…ì…ìe on: …ìe waawataa fe∆¥∆¥ude yeeso, wanaa fii yiltorgol …ìaawo."
  36,68,"Kala mo Men juutni nguurndam mun e yim…ìe …ìen, Men yiltitiray mo …ìaawo. E …ìee kan haqqiltaa? …ìe annda aduna wanaa luttirde, ko saare laakara nden heddotoo?"
  36,69,"Men anndinaali Muhammadu (jom kisiyee) gim…ói; …óum haananaa mo, tawde o yahdaa e mun, sakko he…ìon ka wi'on wonnde ko o yimoowo. Ko Men anndini mo kon wonaali, si wana jantoore e Qur'aanaare …ìanngannde tasko…óoo."
  36,70,"Fii yo jertinir nde, kala laatii…óo wuuru…óo …ìernde, tawde ko on …óon nafitorta nde. Konngol lepte ngol kadi jojja e hoore yeddu…ìe …ìen, tawde hujja nanngirii …ìe jippangol nde ngol, nde yottinee e ma…ì…ìe. hujja woo heddoraaki …ìe, mo …ìe ngantinora."
  36,71,"E …ìe yi'aali, wonnde Men taganii …ìe neemoraa…ói, hara hi…ìe jeyinoo …óin; …ìe wa…óa …ói sottinir…ói haajuuji ma…ì…ìe."
  36,72,"Men eltani …ìe …óin neemoraa…ói, Men wa…óti …ói e sooke ma…ì…ìe: tawi ko e go…ó…ói …óin …ìe wa…ó…óotoo …ìe ronndina, …ìe √±aama e tebbeeli go…ó…ói …óin."
  36,73,"Hino woodani …ìe ton, nafooje goo, hara wanaa wa…ó…óetee…ói …óin e √±aameteeji teew mum tun. ∆äum ko wano lee…ìi baali …óin, e lee…ìi geloo…ói …óin, e lee…ìi be'i …óin e coggeeli majji …óin …ói …ìe mo∆¥∆¥inirta nda…ó…óudi e comci. ∆Åe he…ìoyay ton kadi, nooneeji njaram ka …ìe yaroyta kocce. E …ìee kan yettataa Alla neeminir…óo …ìe …óii neemaaji ekw?"
  36,74,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen jogitorii gaanin Alla rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe, jortagol …ói faaboto …ìe, …ói da…ónda …ìe lepte Alla …óen."
  36,75,"∆äin rewetee…ói …ói ma…ì…ìe, …ói hattanaa faabagol hay ko'e-majji, wanaa fii faabagol reway…ói …ìe …óin acca Alla. Wurin, …óin sanamuuji ko wa…ótidoytee…ói e ma…ì…ìe ka lepte, kala ma…ì…ìe wa…óta da…óndinoraa-de oya."
  36,76,"Wata wiide …ìe : wanaa a Nulaa…óo, maa wonnde ko a yimoowo, ekn fow e mun, wata sunine, an Nulaa…óo. Menen, Me…óen anndi ko …ìe suu…óata e …óum, e ko …ìe fe√±√±inta e mun. Hunnde e mun suu…óaaki Men. Ma Men yo…ìitoy …ìe …óum."
  36,77,"E ne…ó…óanke, yeddu…óo ummital …ìaawo maayde on, miijitaaki, wonnde Men tagirii mo e to…ì…ìere maniiyu? Refti o rewri sagaraaji haa jibinaa o mawni, refti o wonti …óuu…óu…óo yeddondiral e wennjondiral! Kanko o yi'aali …óum, haa o dallinora wonnde ummital wa…óay?"
  36,78,"On yeddu…óo majji, o yejjiti fewndo o dallinoraynoo ∆¥i'e wu…óu…óe …óen, wiide ummital gasataa; wi'ugol: ko hommbo wuurnitata …óe? O yejjitii wonnde o tagano, hari o woodaaka."
  36,79,"An Muhammadu, maakan …ìe ka jaabagol …ìe: wuurnitoowo …óee ∆¥i'e wu…óu…óe, ko tagu…óo …óe On ka laawol aranol. Mo tagii huunde ka arannde mayre, O ronkataa wuurnitude nde. Ko Kanko senii…óo On woni anndu…óo fii kala tagu. Hunnde e fii maggu suu…óaaki Mo."
  36,80,"On wa…óan…óo on, onon yim…ìe …ìen, yiite, iwde e le…ó…óe kecce, tawa ko e majje woni ko hu…ì…ìinirton yiite. Awa faamon, kala waawu…óo hawtude benya- ndirdi …ói…ói (woni hecci…óugol le…ó…óe …óen, e yiite hu…ì…ìinirteenge e majje ngen), ko ha…óttan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ìe."
  36,81,"Kere tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kala mawnu…ói won…ói e majji, On ha…ótanaa wuurnitugol maay…ìe immintina …ìe? ∆äum ko pellet, Himo ha…ótana …óum. Ko Kanko woni ∆äuu…óu…óo tageefo, Tagu…óo kala huunde, Anndu…óo fii majji. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e majji."
  36,82,"Anndon fiyaaku Alla on, si O faandnike wa…óufol huunde, ko O wi'anay nde tun: laato, nde laatora no O yi…óiri non. Hino jeyaa …óum, wiide si O faandike wuurnitugol maa warugol maa immintingol ekn, O wa…óay tun."
  36,83,"Senaade e laa…ìal, woodanii On Mo sirkoo…ìe …ìen askinta ronkugol e Mun! On Mo tawata, ko e juu…óe Makko laamateeri kala huunde woni, Himo wa…óira …óum no O haajiri. Ko e juu…óe Makko soktirgal huunde woni. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon laakara, O yo…ìitoya on njo…ìde golle mon."
